Example on decision making statements - Approximation Checker


#include<stdio.h>
void main(){ float a,b;
	scanf("%f %f",&a,&b);
	if(a-b<=1 && a-b>=-1) printf("Approximate\n");
	else printf("Not approximate\n");
}

/*


Sample Test Cases
Test case 1
49.1 49.6	
Approximate	
Test case 2
18.3 18.9	
Approximate	
Test case 3
26.1 27.3	
Not·approximate	
Test case 4
45.9 48.2	
Not·approximate


*/
